== 应用 ==
西塔疗愈以一种名为“信念工作”的独立会话形式进行，在此过程中，客户和西塔疗愈师面对面就坐或通过电话沟通。西塔疗愈也可以作为日常自我冥想和反省的一种方式。<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Temassız kartları’ kullananlar dikkat!|url=https://www.cnnturk.com/ekonomi/temassiz-kartlari-kullananlar-dikkat|access-date=2020-10-18|website=CNN Türk|language=tr|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830140427/https://www.cnnturk.com/ekonomi/temassiz-kartlari-kullananlar-dikkat|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=‘Temassız kartları’ kullananlar dikkat!|url=https://www.cnnturk.com/ekonomi/temassiz-kartlari-kullananlar-dikkat|access-date=2020-10-18|website=CNN Türk|language=tr|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830140427/https://www.cnnturk.com/ekonomi/temassiz-kartlari-kullananlar-dikkat|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其理念是：参与者可以找到并改变所谓的“信念”，这些信念可能存在于潜意识的核心、遗传、历史和灵魂层面。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />

其目标是改善整体健康并提升幸福感，如Vianna所述，“信念工作使我们有能力消除消极的思维模式，并用积极有益的思维模式取代它们”。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=ThetaHealing: técnica holística e alternativa promete cura energética|url=https://vogue.globo.com/Wellness/noticia/2019/07/thetahealing-tecnica-holistica-e-alternativa-promete-cura-energetica.html|access-date=2020-10-18|website=Vogue|language=pt-br|archive-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025074839/https://vogue.globo.com/Wellness/noticia/2019/07/thetahealing-tecnica-holistica-e-alternativa-promete-cura-energetica.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 理念 ==
Vianna Stibal认为，西塔疗愈的理念围绕“存在的七个层次”展开，这一框架显示出“第七个层次所有事物的创造者”（也称“一个充满爱与智慧的地方”）的重要性。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Theta healing: Latest in alternative therapy clan - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/health-fitness/health-news/Theta-healing-Latest-in-alternative-therapy-clan/articleshow/4845923.cms|access-date=2020-10-18|website=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421075707/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/health-fitness/health-news/Theta-healing-Latest-in-alternative-therapy-clan/articleshow/4845923.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Stibal|first=Vianna|url=https://books.google.de/books?id=gsvNwZhezrsC&printsec=frontcover&hl=de&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=ThetaHealing|publisher=Hay House, Inc|isbn=978-1-4019-2929-9|language=en}}</ref>存在的七个层次解释道，物质和精神世界与原子和粒子的运动有关，而第七个层次则是创造万物的生命力。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Marniemi|first=J.|last2=Parkki|first2=M. G.|date=1975-09-01|title=Radiochemical assay of glutathione S-epoxide transferase and its enhancement by phenobarbital in rat liver in vivo|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9/|journal=Biochemical Pharmacology|volume=24|issue=17|pages=1569–1572|doi=10.1016/0006-2952(75)90080-5|issn=0006-2952|pmid=9|access-date=2020-10-18|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020085501/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，其概念可以与大多数宗教观念相结合。<ref name="#1"/>

